11:44:24:Lustre: DEBUG MARKER: /usr/sbin/lctl mark  recovery-small test_10d: @@@@@@ FAIL: file contents differ 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: recovery-small 10d&lt;/p&gt;</description>
